{
  "video_id": "G5GzWhSgKCE",
  "title": "Create Realistic Character Animation with Ziva Dynamics | SIGGRAPH 2018 | Intel Software",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 51.0,
      "end_time": 550.0,
      "text": "Hi!"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 550.0,
      "end_time": 2380.0,
      "text": "We're at the Intel\nbooth showcasing"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 2380.0,
      "end_time": 4940.0,
      "text": "Ziva Dynamics, the world's\nleading character simulation"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 4940.0,
      "end_time": 6036.0,
      "text": "technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 8680.0,
      "end_time": 12130.0,
      "text": "Ziva technology enables creators\nto make my life-like creatures"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 12130.0,
      "end_time": 13850.0,
      "text": "and characters for film and TV."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 13850.0,
      "end_time": 16660.0,
      "text": "The Intel Xeon servers\nexpand the creative capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 16660.0,
      "end_time": 17727.0,
      "text": "for Ziva's simulations."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 17727.0,
      "end_time": 19810.0,
      "text": "And I'm going to pass it\nover to Lonnie Kraatz who"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 19810.0,
      "end_time": 21920.0,
      "text": "is going to give us a\ndemo of our technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 21920.0,
      "end_time": 24640.0,
      "text": "Ziva's improving the workflow\nand final results of studios"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 24640.0,
      "end_time": 26420.0,
      "text": "all around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 26420.0,
      "end_time": 29230.0,
      "text": "This is a Maya plugin that\nallows studios and indie"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 29230.0,
      "end_time": 31570.0,
      "text": "creators to create more\nrealistic characters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 31570.0,
      "end_time": 34735.0,
      "text": "as seen in \"The Mag,\"\n\"Ghostbusters,\" and \"Suicide"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 34735.0,
      "end_time": 35530.0,
      "text": "Squad.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 35530.0,
      "end_time": 37810.0,
      "text": "So here we have Max,\nour virtual human asset."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 37810.0,
      "end_time": 41500.0,
      "text": "And we have the bones,\nthe muscle, and the skin."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 41500.0,
      "end_time": 43600.0,
      "text": "The bones in this\ncase are the input"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 43600.0,
      "end_time": 47110.0,
      "text": "to the soul, which are\ndriving the muscles, which"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 47110.0,
      "end_time": 48760.0,
      "text": "in turn are driving the skin."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 48760.0,
      "end_time": 53140.0,
      "text": "So if I scrub this, you can\nsee how this stuff interacts."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 53140.0,
      "end_time": 59500.0,
      "text": "And you can see how, a pec\nwould kind of deform differently"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 59500.0,
      "end_time": 60795.0,
      "text": "than the traditional."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 60795.0,
      "end_time": 62170.0,
      "text": "This approach\nallows your muscles"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 62170.0,
      "end_time": 65080.0,
      "text": "to bend, stretch, and flex\nlike they would in real life."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 65080.0,
      "end_time": 68234.0,
      "text": "It's-- we're solving this\nwith real world properties."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 68234.0,
      "end_time": 69650.0,
      "text": "Here's an example\nof our own demo."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 69650.0,
      "end_time": 74995.0,
      "text": "Now if I, just grabbed this arm,\nyou can see that this is just--"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 74995.0,
      "end_time": 78400.0,
      "text": "these bones are being\ndriven by the Maya IK,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 78400.0,
      "end_time": 79720.0,
      "text": "and these ones are solved."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 79720.0,
      "end_time": 83550.0,
      "text": "So if I go back to\nthe start frame,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 83550.0,
      "end_time": 87630.0,
      "text": "you can see this is an\nactual solve in progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 87630.0,
      "end_time": 91060.0,
      "text": "You see the muscles reacting\nto the inputs of the bones."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 91060.0,
      "end_time": 93840.0,
      "text": "And then with that you\ncan change the properties"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 93840.0,
      "end_time": 95590.0,
      "text": "of any of this stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 95590.0,
      "end_time": 103920.0,
      "text": "So I can go into the muscle and\nmake it softer, for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 103920.0,
      "end_time": 105130.0,
      "text": "And there you go."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 107752.0,
      "end_time": 110320.0,
      "text": "So you can kind of see\nhow all this stuff kind of"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 110320.0,
      "end_time": 112270.0,
      "text": "works together."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 112270.0,
      "end_time": 114190.0,
      "text": "Here you can look at--"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 114190.0,
      "end_time": 115780.0,
      "text": "here you see a muscle."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 115780.0,
      "end_time": 118455.0,
      "text": "And if we select\nit, you can barely"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 118455.0,
      "end_time": 122380.0,
      "text": "see the orange little line."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 122380.0,
      "end_time": 126680.0,
      "text": "And that's defining\nthe flow of the fibers."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 126680.0,
      "end_time": 127650.0,
      "text": "So if I go and paint--"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 131690.0,
      "end_time": 135320.0,
      "text": "if I go and paint\nthe fiber endpoint,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 135320.0,
      "end_time": 139970.0,
      "text": "you can see the\ndirection that the fibers"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 139970.0,
      "end_time": 142181.0,
      "text": "are taking by going from\nthe black to the white."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 142181.0,
      "end_time": 143680.0,
      "text": "So now if I were\nto change that, you"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 143680.0,
      "end_time": 145710.0,
      "text": "can see how the fibers\nchange direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 145710.0,
      "end_time": 150840.0,
      "text": "But ultimately that's\ndefining how the muscle fires."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 150840.0,
      "end_time": 152440.0,
      "text": "So when I hit play, that's--"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 152440.0,
      "end_time": 156030.0,
      "text": "that's where\nthey're firing from."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 156030.0,
      "end_time": 157960.0,
      "text": "With Ziva you get\ngreater artistic control"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 157960.0,
      "end_time": 161230.0,
      "text": "over the muscle deformations\nand all material properties."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 161230.0,
      "end_time": 163330.0,
      "text": "To learn more about Ziva,\nyou can check us out"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 163330.0,
      "end_time": 166400.0,
      "text": "online at zivadynamics.com\nor visit the community"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 166400.0,
      "end_time": 169630.0,
      "text": "at community.zivadynamics.com."
    }
  ]
}